name: MYFRIENDSQUIZ
0:
”Alexa, open my quizzy friends”
”Alexa, begin my quizzy friends”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my quizzy friends
des: Welcome to a quiz based on FRIENDS. This quiz contains 10 questions based on FRIENDS sitcom with different difficulty levels. Each question has 3 options. For the right answer you will get 1 point each and it'll add up to your previous score. If you select the wrong answer, your score will remain as it is. You have to select one,two or three as your answer. Let's see if you can crack it !
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
